These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: almond-milk, water
Movie-Genre: romance, drama
Sport: lacrosse, rugby
Transport: roller, skateboard
1. Transport:skateboard is on the left or right of Sport:rugby##3
2. Beverage:water is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:drama == Beverage:almond-milk##1
4. Transport:skateboard is on the right of Transport:roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | water   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama     | romance   |
| Sport         | rugby | lacrosse |
| Transport     | roller | skateboard    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: corn, lettuce
Movie-Genre: horror, fantasy
Pet: turtle, mouse
Transport: ship, snowmobile
1. Pet:mouse is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:horror == Transport:snowmobile##1
3. Food:lettuce is on the right of Movie-Genre:fantasy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | corn     | lettuce |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | horror  |
| Pet           | mouse         | turtle     |
| Transport     | ship   | snowmobile    |

