.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
Job: pilot, mechanic
Nationality: pakistani, turkish
Pet: goat, hedgehog
Sport: weightlifting, ice-hockey
1. Sport:ice-hockey is in an even position##4
2. Nationality:turkish is on the far left or far right##3
3. Job:mechanic == Nationality:pakistani##1
4. Pet:goat is on the left of Nationality:turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | mechanic | pilot    |
| Nationality   | pakistani       | turkish |
| Pet           | goat         | hedgehog    |
| Sport         | weightlifting    | ice-hockey   |

